text: Frost in 2013 John Edward Frost is an Australian theatrical producer. Frost received the JC Williamson Award in 2014. In the 2014 Queen's Birthday Honours he was made a Member of the Order of Australia (AM) for "significant service to the performing arts, particularly as a producer, and as a supporter of industry personnel". == References == Category:Australian theatre managers and producers Category:Helpmann Award winners Category:Living people Category:Members of the Order of Australia Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
